/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Skaros\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Skaros Rock<\/a>. Once there, you will find the ruins of an old <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/venice\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Venetian<\/a> fortress, which was once considered the capital of Santorini. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-skaros-rock.jpg\" alt=\"santorini skaros rock hike\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"santorini skaros rock hike\" class=\"wp-image-59579 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-skaros-rock.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-skaros-rock-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-skaros-rock-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-skaros-rock-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-skaros-rock-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-skaros-rock-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-skaros-rock-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-skaros-rock-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-skaros-rock-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02081928\/santorini-greece-ska