port.jpg\" alt=\"santorini transport atv\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"302\" alt=\"santorini transport atv\" class=\"wp-image-59655 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-800x538.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-1080x726.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-450x302.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-163x110.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-268x180.jpg 268w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-768x516.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-1024x688.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-1440x968.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-600x403.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100327\/santorini-transport.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Locals say an ATV\/Quad is much safer than a motorcycle; however, if you&#x2019;re comfortable and used to a motorcycle, the prices are much lower. Personally, we also find these easier to drive. One great plus about the ATV\/Quad is that it usually has a large trunk to pack your bags while traveling around the island.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-prices-for-renting-an-atv-quad-or-motorcycle-on-santorini\">Prices for renting an ATV\/Quad or Motorcycle on Santorini<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Renting can be done through your hotel or directly at one of the many rental shops. Depending on the season you can expect to pay anywhere from 18 to 30 euros a day for a motorbike and 30 to 45 euros for an ATV\/quad. The more days you rent it for, the more discount you can expect to receive.<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/59555&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04105623\/best-things-to-do-santorini-greece.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\">