00x427.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100359\/santorini-village-Megalochori2-600x854.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100359\/santorini-village-Megalochori2.jpg 1349w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100359\/santorini-village-Megalochori2-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100359\/santorini-village-Megalochori2-569x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-pyrgos\">Pyrgos<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>About 8 kilometers away from Fira is the small and slightly undiscovered village Pyrgos. Here you can find a stunning castle, narrow picturesque streets, and <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/NSbSX2KXuUDpZ51Z9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">panoramic viewpoints<\/a>. In fact, Pyrgos is at the highest point of the island, providing a great view of both sides of Santorini.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Lunch tip:<\/strong> Have lunch at Brusco, a well-decorated cafe in the middle of town.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105140\/santorini-pyrgos.jpg\" alt=\"santorini pyrgos\"><\/noscript><img width=\"255\" height=\"338\" alt=\"santorini pyrgos\" class=\"w