age\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach.jpg\" alt=\"santorini things to do red beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"320\" alt=\"santorini things to do red beach\" class=\"wp-image-59653 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-800x569.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-1080x768.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-450x320.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-163x116.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-253x180.jpg 253w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-768x546.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-1024x729.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-1440x1025.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-300x213.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-600x427.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03100316\/santorini-red-beach.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep in mind that there&#x2019;s a slight danger of falling rocks, as many signs will tell you. Accessing the beach is, therefore, at your own risk. Alternatively, you can visit Red Beach during a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/santorini-boat-tours\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">boat trip<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/santorini-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See all hotels on the island.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__wrapper video-block__wrapper--breakout\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/VideoObject\">\n                <h3 class=\"video-block__wrapper-title\" itemprop=\"name\">Greece<\/h3>\n\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnail\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/18191007\/Thumb-greece-island-hopping-2021-2_1-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Greece\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/18191007\/Thumb-greece-island-hopping-2021-2_1-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2021-06-18 19:07:52\">\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block video-block--mediavine\">\n                    <div class=\"video-block__embed\">\n                        <div class=\"mv-video-target mv-video-id-kfw7hizmfhw1tt8jshdh\" data-video-id=\"kfw7hizmfhw1tt8jshdh\" data-volume=\"70\" data-ratio=\"16:9\" data-autoinsert=\"true\" data-disable-jsonld=\"true\"><\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <a class=\"video-block__credit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/c\/saltinourhair?sub_confirmation=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"YouTube Salt in our Hair\">\n                    <div class=\"socials__item\">\n                        <span class=\"socials__link\">\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-youtube\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-youtube\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <span>Subscribe to our <b>YouTube channel<\/b> and never miss a video!<\/span>\n                <\/a>\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__bg\">\n                    <img class=\"video-block__bg-image lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/18191007\/Thumb-greece-island-hopping-2021-2_1-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Greece\" height=\"450\" width=\"800\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-10-go-on-a-wine-tour\">10. Go on a wine tour&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The assyrtiko wines of the Greek Islands are well-loved for their unique taste. Instead of growing the vines vertically, they are grown in baskets on the ground. This allows the vines to tap into the volcanic soil that contains moisture instead of needing to be watered (water is a scarce resource on the island). <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-1080x762.jpg\" alt=\"winery santorini\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"317\" alt=\"winery santorini\" class=\"wp-image-59632 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-1080x762.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-800x564.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-450x317.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-163x115.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-255x180.jpg 255w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-768x542.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-1024x722.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-1440x1016.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-600x423.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082747\/santorini-wine-tour1-1080x762.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The yield of wineries is low, making it a more exclusive wine. Growing them in this way also provides more coverage against the island&#x2019;s notoriously strong winds.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082807\/santorini-wine-tour3-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"wine tour\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"wine tour\" class=\"wp-image-59636 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082807\/santorini-wine-tour3-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082807\/santorini-wine-tour3-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082807\/santorini-wine-tour3-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082807\/santorini-wine-tour3-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082807\/santorini-wine-tour3-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082807\/santorini-wine-tour3-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03