lock-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-gaia-wines\">Gaia Wines<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>We booked a wine tour on Santorini at <a href=\"https:\/\/gaiawines.gr\/en\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Gaia Wines<\/a>, and it was much more interesting than initially expected. Besides having a tasting experience, we also learned about harvest and the chemical reaction during the wine-aging process. The wine tastings can be paired with a platter of local cheeses and bread at their uniquely located terrace &#x2013; right by the sea under the shade of trees. Bliss!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082757\/santorini-wine-tour2-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"santorini greece wine tour\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"santorini greece wine tour\" class=\"wp-image-59634 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082757\/santorini-wine-tour2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082757\/santorini-wine-tour2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082757\/santorini-wine-tour2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082757\/santorini-wine-tour2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082757\/santorini-wine-tour2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082757\/santorini-wine-tour2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03082757\/santorini-wine-tour2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c