erissa Beach<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you done all the things to do in Santorini? Or maybe you&#x2019;re simply wanting a day of relaxation? Head over to the black sand beach, lined with umbrellas, named Perissa Beach. The beach is a long stretch of sand with many comfortable beds, sat below the restaurants situated on the other side of the street. Perissa village is a popular seaside resort that mainly attracts young people and backpackers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-1080x810.jpg\" alt=\"santorini beaches\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"santorini beaches\" class=\"wp-image-59667 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-1440x1080.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-600x450.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/03105129\/santorini-beaches-1080x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Either rent a bed for the day or pick a free spot to put your towel down. Once you&#x2019;re comfortable, sit back and enjoy the sunshine and a refreshing swim in the Santorini sea.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Did you know?<\/strong> Regular sunscreens are toxic for the corals and animals in the sea. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reef-safe-sunscreen\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Learn about reef-safe sunscreen<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"