\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/02100445\/santorini-restaurants-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\">How to visit Santorini<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There&#x2019;s no surprise that Santorini, and all its many things to do, attract a lot of visitors. In 2019 alone, the small island, with a population of only 15,500 people, received over 2 million tourists!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia.jpg\" alt=\"santorini things to do oia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"santorini things to do oia\" class=\"wp-image-59739 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090733\/santorini-things-to-do-oia.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-to-santorini\">Getting to Santorini<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-ferry\">Ferry<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Santorini Island is well connected with daily ferries from the mainland (Athens) and many other nearby islands like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/greece\/milos\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Milos<\/a> or Mykonos. The ferries are fast, comfortable, and generally faster than flying from nearby destinations (especially, if you count the time it takes to check-in). During the high season, from March to October, there are also direct ferries to other popular islands.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ferryhopper.com\/en\/?aff_uid=slthr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Check the ferry tickets and prices here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04082543\/santorini-transport2.jpg\" alt=\"santorini greece ferry\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"santorini greece ferry\" class=\"wp-image-59713 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04082543\/santorini-transport2.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04082543\/santorini-transport2-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04082543\/santorini-transport2-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04082543\/santorini-transport2-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04082543\/santorini-transport2-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04082543\/santorini-transport2-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04082543\/santorini-transport2-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04082543\/santorini-transport2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04082543\/santorini-transport2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\