 the island in just a couple of days, however, we would recommend 4-nights\/5-days as the perfect length for all the things to do in Santorini.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"things to do santorini greece\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do santorini greece\" class=\"wp-image-59755 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04095926\/greece-travel-guide-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-