ion. Additionally, cars will come with AC, which is an advantage over being exposed to the sun on the ATV. There are many car rental locations on Santorini Island. For example, Santorini Airport, the port, or within the larger villages.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s recommended to book a rental car ahead of your trip, particularly during the high season. During this time, if you leave it until the last minute, you might not find an available rental car.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Rent a car at a local car company through <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-greece\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>. When booking through them, all insurances are included. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-greece\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-public-transport-in-santorini\">Public transport in Santorini<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>A great, and definitely the cheapest, way of getting around Santorini is to use the local buses. You can get a bus to pretty much anywhere on the island but you always have to use Fira (capital city) as the hub for all transfers. Therefore, if you&#x2019;re planning to use the bus, we recommend getting a hotel in Fira too.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A one-way ticket costs about 2 euros and the timetable per destination can be found on the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.e-ktel.com\/en\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">operator&#x2019;s website<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport.jpg\" alt=\"santorini public transport\"><\/noscript><img width=\"438\" height=\"338\" alt=\"santorini public transport\" class=\"wp-image-59737 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-778x600.jpg 778w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-1051x810.jpg 1051w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-438x338.jpg 438w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-163x126.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-234x180.jpg 234w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-768x592.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-1024x789.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-1401x1080.jpg 1401w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-1868x1440.jpg 1868w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04090720\/santorini-public-transport-300x231.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.salt