xury easily exceeding that. Don&#x2019;t worry, there an option for every kind of budget. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/santorini-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all hotels on the island<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-budget-hotels-70-usd-night\">Budget hotels&#xA0;(~70 USD\/night)<\/h3>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/santorini-ambience-suites\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04085500\/ambience-santorini-hotel-30x20.jpeg\" alt=\"Ambience Suites\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04085500\/ambience-santorini-hotel-450x300.jpeg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">Ambience Suites<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/loizos-santorini-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04085453\/loizos-santorini-hotel-30x20.jpeg\" alt=\"Loizos Residences\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/04085453\/loizos-sant